title: Verify student can access the skyfactor application
custom_steps:
Given I am on skyfactor login page
When I login into the application with "<UserName>" and "<Password>"
Then Student land on Overview page

Examples:
|UserName|Password|
|qanupur@mailinator.com|Qait@123|

title: Verify user can create Static List
custom_preconds:
Given I am on skyfactor login page
When I login into the application with "<UserName>" and "<Password>"
Then Student land on Overview page

Examples:
|UserName|Password|
|qanupur@mailinator.com|Qait@123|
custom_steps:
Given I am on "<Overview_Page>" page
When I click on "<StaticList_Tab>" tab
And I click on Create New List button on static lists page
Then I am able to create Static List with "<StaticList_Name>" and "<StaticList_Description>"
And I am able to view created static List in list
	
Examples:
| StaticList_Name | StaticList_Description | StaticList_Tab | Overview_Page |
| Static List | StaticList Description | Static Lists |#/overview |

title: Verify user can edit Static List
custom_steps:
Given I am on "<StaticList_Page>" page
When I edit Static List with "<StaticList_Name>" and "<StaticList_Description>"
Then I am able to view the edited static List on the page
	
Examples:
| StaticList_Page |StaticList_Name|StaticList_Description|
| #/static-lists |Edited StaticList|Edited Description|

title: Verify user can delete Static List
custom_steps:
Given I am on "<StaticList_Page>" page
When I click on "<StaticList_Tab>" tab
When I delete the static List with "<StaticList_Name>"
Then I am not able to view the deleted static List on page
	
Examples:
| StaticList_Page |StaticList_Name|StaticList_Tab|
| #/static-lists |Edited StaticList|Static Lists|
